l took your things up
to your room.

19
00:02:11,266 --> 00:02:12,669
Thank you.

20
00:02:18,708 --> 00:02:20,243
Here we are...

21
00:02:20,877 --> 00:02:23,315
lf you had told us

22
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:26,352
that you were coming
a little sooner

23
00:02:26,516 --> 00:02:28,419
we'd have taken time off.

24
00:02:28,585 --> 00:02:31,390
lt's a miracle
l managed to get away.

25
00:02:31,554 --> 00:02:33,491
But l have to work too.

26
00:02:33,656 --> 00:02:36,194
- To your visit!
- Can't you take 10 days off

27
00:02:36,359 --> 00:02:40,200
No, just before l lea,
they gave me a great project.

28
00:02:40,363 --> 00:02:42,934
l'd have cancelled.

29
00:02:43,099 --> 00:02:47,240
l didn't want to.
l wanted to see you.

30
00:02:51,174 --> 00:02:55,015
This is for you both.

31
00:03:06,089 --> 00:03:10,564
l don't take photos.
Your father can have it.

32
00:03:13,864 --> 00:03:15,499
ls it a digital one?

33
