Yes, it's very easy to use.
The definition is wonderful.

34
00:03:20,471 --> 00:03:22,474
l don't understand a word.

35
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:26,381
You could take photos
of the garden. It's beautiful.

36
00:03:26,544 --> 00:03:29,650
The garden's your mother.

37
00:03:31,715 --> 00:03:34,554
No, if you feed him,
we'll never get any peace.

38
00:03:34,718 --> 00:03:36,288
l can't believe that...

39
00:03:36,454 --> 00:03:37,789
That's enough!

40
00:03:39,256 --> 00:03:41,693
No, Tiger, come here!

41
00:03:41,859 --> 00:03:44,931
Michel, you could
try training him.

42
00:03:45,096 --> 00:03:47,768
We could have him put down too.

43
00:04:34,045 --> 00:04:36,683
- You can't sleep?
- No.

44
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:42,324
- Want a sleeping pill?
- No thanks.

45
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:44,539
Everything ok?

46
00:07:44,706 --> 00:07:47,310
l can't concentrate in my room.

47
00:07:47,474 --> 00:07:50,213
There's a lot of bronchitis about.

48
00:07:51,478 --> 00:07:55,052
l passed Grand dad's house earlier.
It's empty, isn't it?

49
00:07:55,216 --> 00:07:57,554
lt's uninhabitable.

50
00:07:58,453 --> 00:08:00,390
l can't get anything done here.

51
00:08:00,555 --> 00:08:01,990
You just got here!

52
00:08:02,156 --> 00:08:07,199
Relax for a couple of days,
then get back to your work.

53
00:08:08,763 --> 00:08:12,136
You always asked me
to go to Granddad's with you,

54
00:08:12,301 --> 00:08:16,175
as if to avoid being
alone with him.

55
00:08:19,607 --> 00:08:22,779
l took you
because he wanted to see you.

56
00:08:24,011 --> 00:08:26,816
He was fond of you.

57
00:08:26,982 --> 00:08:30,555
He always asked about you.
You know that.

58
00:08:32,254 --> 00:08:35,928
So he'd be happy to see me
in his house.

59
00:08:39,161 --> 00:08:41,198
l couldn't come to the funeral.

60
00:08:41,363 --> 00:08:43,533
l really couldn't get away

61
00:08:43,698 --> 00:08:46,905
and I’m sorry that l wasn't with you.

62
00:08:47,069 --> 00:08:49,741
I’ve worked a lot
these last for years. Sorry.

63
00:08:49,905 --> 00:08:51,507
This wasn't planned either.

64
00:08:51,673 --> 00:08:54,444
The engineer just found
a clever way

65
00:08:54,610 --> 00:08:56,279
to save even more water.

66
00:08:56,444 --> 00:08:59,884
lt's a really great project.
Sorry, but l need quiet.

67
00:09:00,048 --> 00:09:02,553
You sound like an old maid.

68
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:09,393
Right, l'll get back to work.

69
00:09:11,326 --> 00:09:15,468
The keys are in the kitchen,
the ring with Tintin's rocket.

70
00:10:15,959 --> 00:10:18,129
- We'll deliver tomorrow.
- Thank you.

71
00:10:27,804 --> 00:10:30,041
You scared me!

72
00:10:31,342 --> 00:10:32,811
Aren't you working?

73
00:10:32,976 --> 00:10:35,581
Yes, but l close at seven.

74
00:10:35,745 --> 00:10:37,882
lt's already seven?

75
00:10:38,047 --> 00:10:40,252
l haven't stopped.

76
00:10:40,417 --> 00:10:42,387
l came to see
if you were comfortable.

77
00:10:42,552 --> 00:10:44,789
You don't waste time.

78
00:10:46,056 --> 00:10:48,493
- Want a coffee?
- No thanks.

79
00:10:49,527 --> 00:10:51,731
Will you have room to work?

80
00:10:51,896 --> 00:10:54,935
Are you making fun?

81
00:10:55,099 --> 00:10:59,474
No, I’m glad to see
someone living here.

82
00:11:00,437 --> 00:11:04,378
Even if l'd prefer to see you
staying with us.

83
00:11:07,244 --> 00:11:08,780
ls life good?

84
00:11:08,946 --> 00:11:11,050
Of course. Why?

85
00:11:11,649 --> 00:11:13,084
l don't know.

86
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:17,391
You seem like
you want to avoid us.

87
00:11:17,556 --> 00:11:18,491
Got problems?

88
00:11:18,656 --> 00:11:22,029
Not at all.
l came here to see you, l swear.

89
00:11:22,192 --> 00:11:25,566
But l have to work too,
make phone calls at night...

90
00:11:25,729 --> 00:11:29,135
I’ve been in Toronto 10 years
and you've never been over.

91
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:33,642
lf it were up to me,
we'd have come long ago.

92
00:11:33,804 --> 00:11:37,035
lf you insisted,
maybe she'd fly for once.

93
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:40,800
No, l don't think so.

94
00:11:40,935 --> 00:11:46,322
Last year, l got us tickets
to go to Florence by train.

95
00:11:46,484 --> 00:11:48,187
At the last minute,

96
00:11:48,353 --> 00:11:51,292
l found her sitting next to
her bag, refusing to leave.

97
00:11:51,456 --> 00:11:53,226
With her father's illness,

98
00:11:53,391 --> 00:11:55,996
even going to Bordeaux
stressed her.

99
00:11:56,161 --> 00:11:59,433
Apart from work,
nothing interests her.

100
00:12:18,316 --> 00:12:21,055
- You can't leave it here!
- Suzanne...

101
00:12:21,219 --> 00:12:23,156
Don't shout.
It's a delivery for me.

102
00:12:23,321 --> 00:12:24,156
Hello. l won't take long.

103
00:12:24,322 --> 00:12:26,860
l couldn't have known.

104
00:12:27,025 --> 00:12:29,329
lt holds for you too, you know.

105
00:12:29,495 --> 00:12:32,667
Parking here
is strictly forbidden.

106
00:12:32,831 --> 00:12:34,066
All right.

107
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:38,538
Mind out.

108
00:12:49,181 --> 00:12:54,291
This is no good at all.
There's no hook-up.

109
00:12:54,453 --> 00:12:56,490
The pipes need changing.

110
00:12:56,656 --> 00:12:58,926
The dish washer
was a bad idea then.

111
00:12:59,091 --> 00:13:02,130
lt'll take years to redo it,
right?

112
00:13:02,727 --> 00:13:04,831
lt's a day's work for a plumber.

113
00:13:04,997 --> 00:13:09,205
l could try to help out
but this needs a professional.

114
00:13:09,368 --> 00:13:11,405
Thank you. l'll manage.

115
00:13:11,570 --> 00:13:13,373
I’m sorry.

116
00:13:13,539 --> 00:13:14,707
Let's go.

