Suzanne, thank you for the fruit.

120
00:15:28,743 --> 00:15:31,615
There's far too much of it for me.

121
00:15:33,281 --> 00:15:38,057
And l prefer to pick it
before the birds gorge on it.

122
00:15:38,219 --> 00:15:40,089
lf someone can use it...

123
00:15:40,254 --> 00:15:42,091
That's kind.

